text: Julia Karin Ormond (born 4 January 1965 in Surrey, England) is an English actress. She starred in many movies, including Nostradamus, First Knight, Legends of the Fall and Sabrina. She also starred on television shows, including Nurse Jackie and Temple Grandin. Category:English movie actors Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Surrey
title: Julia Ormond
